---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Om oss — Begbilnorr Luleå | Din trygga bilhandlare"
  description="Begbilnorr i Luleå — din trygga bilhandlare sedan 2018. Kvalitetskontrollerade bilar med garanti och personlig service i Norrbotten."
>
  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-label">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        VEM ÄR VI
      </div>
      <h1>Om Begbilnorr</h1>
      <p>Din trygga bilhandlare i Luleå sedan 2018</p>
      <div class="hero-line"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <section class="about-content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-two-col">
        <div class="about-text">
          <h2>Vår historia</h2>
          <p>Begbilnorr bildades 2018 med en enkel vision: att erbjuda kvalitetskontrollerade begagnade bilar med garanti och personlig service till kunderna i Norrbotten.</p>
          <p>Idag har vi vuxit till att bli en av de mest pålitliga bilhandlarna i Luleå. Vi har sålt hundratals bilar och hjälpt tusentals kunder att hitta sin drömbil -- alltid med trygghet och transparens i fokus.</p>
          <p>Vi tror på långsiktiga relationer med våra kunder. Därför erbjuder vi alltid garanti, finansiering och personlig uppföljning efter köpet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image-placeholder" style="padding:0;overflow:hidden;">
          <img src="/images/showroom.webp" alt="Begbilnorr showroom med begagnade bilar i Luleå" width="900" height="1200" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="stats-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">14+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">År i branschen</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">150+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Bilar per år</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">2000+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Nöjda kunder</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Garanti på alla bilar</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label" style="text-align:center;">VÅRA VÄRDERINGAR</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;">Våra värderingar</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <!-- shield-check -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Kvalitet</h3>
          <p>Varje bil genomgår en noggrann kontroll innan den erbjuds till försäljning. Vi kompromissar aldrig med kvaliteten och säkerställer att du får en bil du kan lita på.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <!-- eye -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Transparens</h3>
          <p>Inga dolda kostnader eller överraskningar. Vi är alltid ärliga och öppna om bilens historik, skick och pris. Du ska alltid veta exakt vad du betalar för.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <!-- heart-handshake -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/><path d="M12 5 9.04 7.96a2.17 2.17 0 0 0 0 3.08c.82.82 2.13.85 3 .07l2.07-1.9a2.82 2.82 0 0 1 3.79 0l2.96 2.66"/><path d="m18 15-2-2"/><path d="m15 18-2-2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Kundnöjdhet</h3>
          <p>Din trygghet är vår prioritet. Vi erbjuder garanti, finansiering och personlig service för att göra ditt bilköp så smidigt och tryggt som möjligt.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="team-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label" style="text-align:center;">VÅRT TEAM</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="text-align:center;">Möt teamet</h2>
      <p class="team-subtitle">Personerna bakom Begbilnorr som jobbar för att ge dig bästa möjliga upplevelse</p>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Anton Fredriksson</h3>
          <div class="team-role">Säljare</div>
          <p class="team-desc">Anton hjälper dig hitta rätt bil utifrån dina behov och budget. Han guidar dig genom hela köpprocessen på ett personligt och professionellt sätt.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Rizwan Aslam</h3>
          <div class="team-role">Hallvärd</div>
          <p class="team-desc">Rizwan ser till att vår hall och alla bilar alltid är i toppskick, redo för visning och leverans med högsta standard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Arsal Seemab</h3>
          <div class="team-role">Säljare</div>
          <p class="team-desc">Arsal brinner för att ge varje kund en trygg och smidig bilaffär. Han hittar den perfekta bilen till rätt pris.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location -->
  <section class="location-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label" style="text-align:center;">BESÖK OSS</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;">Hitta oss</h2>
      <div class="location-grid">
        <div class="map-placeholder" style="padding:0;">
          <img src="/images/hitta-oss.webp" alt="Begbilnorr bilhandlare sett uppifrån i Luleå" width="1200" height="1200" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="location-info">
          <div class="location-item">
            <div class="loc-icon">
              <!-- map-pin icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="loc-text">
              <h4>Adress</h4>
              <p><a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Fabriksv%C3%A4gen+18,+972+54+Lule%C3%A5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fabriksvägen 18, 972 54 Luleå</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="location-item">
            <div class="loc-icon">
              <!-- phone icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="loc-text">
              <h4>Telefon</h4>
              <a href="tel:0920-99986">0920-999 86</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="location-item">
            <div class="loc-icon">
              <!-- mail icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="loc-text">
              <h4>E-post</h4>
              <a href="mailto:info@begbilnorr.se">info@begbilnorr.se</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="location-item">
            <div class="loc-icon">
              <!-- clock icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="loc-text">
              <h4>Öppettider</h4>
              <p>Måndag - Fredag: 09:00 - 18:00</p>
              <p>Lördag - Söndag: 10:00 - 18:00</p>
              <p style="font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">Vi rekommenderar att boka tid på helger</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>Redo att hitta din nästa bil?</h2>
      <p>Bläddra bland våra kvalitetskontrollerade bilar eller kontakta oss för personlig rådgivning.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/bilar" class="btn-primary">Se alla bilar</a>
        <a href="tel:0920-99986" class="btn-outline">Ring oss</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content-section {
    background: var(--bg-dark-2);
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .about-two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-image-placeholder {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark-5) 0%, var(--bg-dark-4) 100%);
    border-radius: 8px;
    min-height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-image-placeholder::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 4px;
    background: var(--red);
  }

  /* Stats */
  .stats-section {
    background: var(--bg-dark-3);
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Values */
  .values-section {
    background: var(--bg-dark-2);
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--bg-dark-3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 40px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(230,46,45,0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .value-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(230,46,45,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    color: var(--red);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .value-card:hover .value-icon {
    background: var(--red);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Team */
  .team-section {
    background: var(--bg-dark-3);
    padding: 100px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .team-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .team-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    background: var(--bg-dark-2);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .team-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: rgba(230,46,45,0.3);
  }

  .team-avatar {
    width: 130px;
    height: 130px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark-5, #2a2a2a) 0%, var(--bg-dark-4, #222) 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  .team-avatar::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--red);
  }

  .team-card h3 {
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .team-card .team-role {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--red);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .team-card .team-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Location */
  .location-section {
    background: var(--bg-dark-2);
    padding: 100px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .location-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .map-placeholder {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark-5, #2a2a2a) 0%, var(--bg-dark-4, #222) 100%);
    border-radius: 8px;
    height: 380px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .map-placeholder::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--red);
  }

  .map-placeholder .placeholder-icon {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .map-placeholder .placeholder-icon span {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .location-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .location-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: var(--bg-dark-3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .location-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: rgba(230,46,45,0.3);
  }

  .loc-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(230,46,45,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .loc-text h4 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .loc-text p,
  .loc-text a {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .loc-text a {
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .loc-text a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--bg-dark-3);
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-two-col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .team-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .location-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .team-avatar {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }

    .map-placeholder {
      height: 260px;
    }
  }
</style>
